Let scrape the skyscrapers using Scrapy

100 Tallest Completed Buildings in the World by Height to Architectural Top

Tallest now is Burj Khalifa

Scrapy can help

Statistics about these 100 skyscrapers:

  • Usages
    • 40 are multipurpose.
    • 74 are used for office.
    • 43 are used for hotel.
    • 29 are used for residential.
    • 2 are used for retail.

  • Totals
    • 7758 floors.
    • 118653 feet.

Time

  • 46 do not have Proposed Year listed.
  • 3 do not have Construction Start Year listed.
  • From Proposed To Construction Start:
    • Cannot compute 46.
    • Shortest took 0 year.
    • Longest took 9 year.
  • From Construction Start To Complete:
    • Cannot compute 3.
    • Shortest took 1 year.
    • Longest took 11 year.

One year to build a skyscraper! Really?
